{"tid":1714720,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"返學返工下場，中在圈套（有圖）","createTime":"2019-11-13T02:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T02:50:02.000Z","uid":73857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"37eb1a43dc164de0ecd124bc8b284689c209fc88","tid":1714720,"uid":73857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HRp7j0Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHRp7j0Z.png&h=3a1cb335&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLZbMF3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLZbMF3.png&h=27495473&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b71905fbb5837aa200bb6e7266dd0d60f27898b6","tid":1714720,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:42:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"0a31dc99406b4ce8ffd73e2bf6e1944715d1f932","tid":1714720,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201